      <p class="text-lg opacity-80">日々を整える、小さな習慣</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-three-beige w-full max-w-lg rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-2xl text-three-dark transform hover:rotate-1 transition duration-300">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8 border-b border-three-dark/10 pb-3">
        <p class="font-bold text-xl">2026 / 01 / 25</p>
        <p class="italic font-bold opacity-40 text-sm">Sun.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-lg font-bold">
