          <span class="opacity-30">1.</span>
          <p class="italic flex-grow">朝、お気に入りのコーヒーをゆっくり飲めた。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start border-l-4 border-three-dark/20 pl-4">
          <span class="opacity-30">2.</span>
          <p class="italic flex-grow">デザインの反映がスムーズにできた！</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start border-l-4 border-three-dark/20 pl-4">
          <span class="opacity-30">3.</span>
          <p class="italic flex-grow">新しいスタートを切ることができた。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-three-beige py-10 text-center">
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 mb-4">
      <%= link_to "利用規約", "#", class: "text-xs font-bold text-three-dark opacity-60 hover:opacity-100" %>
      <%= link_to "プライバシーポリシー", "#", class: "text-xs font-bold text-three-dark opacity-60 hover:opacity-100" %>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-three-dark opacity-40 uppercase tracking-widest">&copy; 2026 Three - Write your 3 goods.</p>
  </footer>

